# Adversarial Pickle Corpus Scan
Output demos/adversarial-corpus.gif
Set Shell zsh
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 800
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 40ms

Type "export PYTHONPATH=$PWD/python"
Enter
Sleep 300ms

Type "# Adversarial Pickle Corpus — 46 test samples"
Enter
Sleep 800ms

Type "ls tests/adversarial_corpus/ghsa_pickles/ | head -15"
Enter
Sleep 1.5s

Type "sentinel artifact tests/adversarial_corpus/"
Enter
Sleep 8s

Type ""
Sleep 2s
